{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2021/gatsby-blog/4/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Woo, Jeongmin"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"10412c32-dcc9-58e0-9ed6-ee9cc7ca3e88","excerpt":"도메인을 구매하여 깃허브 페이지에 연결하는 방법을 소개합니다. 도메인 등록 가비아에서 구매했습니다. DNS도 해당 업체의 서비스를 이용했습니다. A 레코드 설정 해당 도메인의 DNS 레코드 관리 설정에서 ,  혹은  레코드를 생성합니다.  레코드를 생성하기 위해 다음 IP…","html":"<p>도메인을 구매하여 깃허브 페이지에 연결하는 방법을 소개합니다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"도메인-등록\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%8F%84%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8-%EB%93%B1%EB%A1%9D\" aria-label=\"도메인 등록 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>도메인 등록</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.gabia.com/\">가비아</a>에서 구매했습니다. DNS도 해당 업체의 서비스를 이용했습니다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"a-레코드-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#a-%EB%A0%88%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"a 레코드 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>A 레코드 설정</h2>\n<p>해당 도메인의 DNS 레코드 관리 설정에서 <code class=\"language-text\">ALIAS</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">ANAME</code> 혹은 <code class=\"language-text\">A</code> 레코드를 생성합니다. <code class=\"language-text\">A</code> 레코드를 생성하기 위해 <a href=\"https://docs.github.com/en/pages/configuring-a-custom-domain-for-your-github-pages-site/managing-a-custom-domain-for-your-github-pages-site\">다음 IP 주소</a>를 추가합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">185.199.108.153\n185.199.109.153\n185.199.110.153\n185.199.111.153</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d309859c100375fedf2a420d3fb0f0d4/9eaa0/4_dns_records.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 31.0126582278481%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"DNS Records\"\n        title=\"DNS Records\"\n        src=\"/static/d309859c100375fedf2a420d3fb0f0d4/f058b/4_dns_records.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d309859c100375fedf2a420d3fb0f0d4/c26ae/4_dns_records.png 158w,\n/static/d309859c100375fedf2a420d3fb0f0d4/6bdcf/4_dns_records.png 315w,\n/static/d309859c100375fedf2a420d3fb0f0d4/f058b/4_dns_records.png 630w,\n/static/d309859c100375fedf2a420d3fb0f0d4/40601/4_dns_records.png 945w,\n/static/d309859c100375fedf2a420d3fb0f0d4/78612/4_dns_records.png 1260w,\n/static/d309859c100375fedf2a420d3fb0f0d4/9eaa0/4_dns_records.png 1676w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"gatsby-plugin-cname으로-cname-생성하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gatsby-plugin-cname%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-cname-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"gatsby plugin cname으로 cname 생성하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-plugin-cname으로 CNAME 생성하기</h2>\n<p>Github Pages를 통해 배포를 하다보면 <a href=\"https://github.com/tschaub/gh-pages/issues/213\">Github Pages에서 설정한 커스텀 도메인이 초기화되는 문제</a>가 발생합니다. Github가 CNAME 파일을 참고하기 때문인데요. CNAME을 생성하는데는 다음과 같은 방법들이 있습니다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">public</code> 폴더에 <code class=\"language-text\">CNAME</code> 파일 생성</li>\n<li>npm 스크립트에 <code class=\"language-text\">echo &quot;customdomain.com&quot; &gt; build/CNAME</code> 추가</li>\n<li><strong>gatsby-plugin-cname 사용</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>그 중 첫번째와 두번째 방법은 커스텀 도메인이 바뀔 때마다 직접 수정을 해야하는 불편함이 있습니다. <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/plugins/gatsby-plugin-cname/\">gatsby-plugin-cname</a>은 <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code>에서 siteUrl을 읽어와 자동으로 CNAME을 생성해주는 플러그인입니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>설치</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install gatsby-plugin-cname</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"적용\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9\" aria-label=\"적용 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>적용</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code> 파일에 다음을 추가합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">gatsby-config.js</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  siteMetadata<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    siteUrl<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'https://your.custom.domain/'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">'gatsby-plugin-cname'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>이제 <code class=\"language-text\">npm run deploy</code>로 배포 시, <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code> 파일의 siteUrl을 읽어 자동으로 CNAME이 생성됩니다.</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/2021/gatsby-blog/4/#%EB%8F%84%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8-%EB%93%B1%EB%A1%9D\">도메인 등록</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2021/gatsby-blog/4/#a-%EB%A0%88%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\">A 레코드 설정</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/2021/gatsby-blog/4/#gatsby-plugin-cname%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-cname-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">gatsby-plugin-cname으로 CNAME 생성하기</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/2021/gatsby-blog/4/#%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\">설치</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2021/gatsby-blog/4/#%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9\">적용</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Gatsby 블로그 개발 일지 - 4. 깃허브 페이지에 커스텀 도메인 적용하기","date":"April 18, 2021","description":null,"tags":["Gatsby"]}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2021/discord-stat-bot/0/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"discord.js를 활용한 디스코드 봇 만들기"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2021/error-log/20210620_useselector_returns_undefined/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[에러 로그] React-redux useSelector의 undefined 반환"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"10412c32-dcc9-58e0-9ed6-ee9cc7ca3e88","previousPostId":"a01693eb-ab49-5400-bd7e-900ea97d24a5","nextPostId":"2937bb31-af4f-5084-be5d-cb7600f98e83"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3518605037"]}